    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/b693641e8ebbc1eb92afd432e3aeff37.poster.avif?t=1661251871\" width=682 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/b693641e8ebbc1eb92afd432e3aeff37.webm?t=1661251871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/b693641e8ebbc1eb92afd432e3aeff37.mp4?t=1661251871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>某日，名叫风岱宗的男子阴阳差错地来到了地府，并被地府的审判官们宣判已死的事实。离奇的是风岱宗并没有印象自己是怎么死亡的，不记得自己曾经和谁有过什么恩怨，也几乎没有和谁发生过什么严重的冲突。他问判官，「我是怎么死的？」对方先是沉默，然后简单说明是死于意外的事故，甚至连罪行都没有说到。被押往极刑的路途中，他趁乱逃脱，在江边遇见了一位正在垂钓的老人，老人告诉他，想要返阳只有一个办法......<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/140fad3bc9ebfe559a6feb95741b151f.poster.avif?t=1661251871\" width=682 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/140fad3bc9ebfe559a6feb95741b151f.webm?t=1661251871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/140fad3bc9ebfe559a6feb95741b151f.mp4?t=1661251871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>有适合入门和老手的难度，让所有人享受闪躲与攻击的快感！<br>不只是华丽的弹幕效果，每个关卡都有不同风格的战斗！<br>充满个性的角色与跌宕起伏的故事，无处不是防不胜防的梗！<br>全新的特殊水墨风格，让角色典雅却不死板！<br>丰富的搜集要素，尽管探索所有的成就还有隐藏要素！<br>收集轶闻卷轴，一窥阎王私下秘闻！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/ebd2402af311abbadfe2be03303a741c.avif?t=1661251871\" width=622 height=100 /></span><br>专门掌管人间生死簿，管理阴间受刑吉凶。阴魂来到本殿，引上殿右的孽镜台，凡属善人者，令接引往生天堂或极乐世界；善恶参半者，按其业力送交十殿投胎转世；恶多善少者，押送其余各殿审判，令受各种刑法。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/62d0a7a723f8687cb381a8f6a9a38068.avif?t=1661251871\" width=622 height=100 /></span><br>专门掌管在阳间不信因果、阻人行善、毁僧谤道等罪。阴魂来到本殿，可以登上望乡台，眺望家中情况，一解思乡之苦。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/3f2670bcadd8cb1707869b1fb001e479.avif?t=1661251871\" width=622 height=100 /></span><br>掌管大海之底、正东方沃焦石下的合大地狱，此狱宽广八千里，并另设十六小地狱专门掌管在阳间瞒税不缴、耍赖欠租、交易欺诈等罪。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/8df02f1c8e6cdef4e9531a87f0d78f2e.avif?t=1661251871\" width=622 height=100 /></span><br>阎罗王之亲信，为了分担阎王的工作量，绝大多的琐事皆由公孙氏操刀，小至生活起居，大至审判之事。平时在判桌旁宣示堕入者之业障罪刑，口齿清晰精明，其威严不逊于拍案的判官。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/af5def9daebcd57d2cfccb1c8e379521.avif?t=1661251871\" width=622 height=100 /></span><br>因枉死而来到地府的普通上班族，虽然想了解自己的死因，但总是得到奇怪的回应。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/25d875c08c43c041c1371a701659e86f.avif?t=1661251871\" width=622 height=100 /></span><br>奈河旁垂钓的善良老人，他并非罪人也非失落落魄的亡魂，一身轻装实在与气氛沉重的地府不对调，沉稳的说话风格还有吊诡的话题，让人感受得出一股神秘且强大的气息。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/83f9513a7ec0426d6aafca4b30dda7f7.avif?t=1661251871\" width=610 height=360 /></span><br>方向键:移动<br>Z:射击<br>X:使用法器<br>C:炸弹<br>shift:集中模式/慢速模式<br>ctrl:切换法器<br>ESC:暂停<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/3171bba096472ffccf3cfee95bd3d05f.avif?t=1661251871\" width=610 height=360 /></span><br>L3:移动<br>□:射击<br>○:确认<br>Χ:切换法器/取消<br>R1:使用法器<br>R2:炸弹<br>L1:集中模式/慢速模式<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/e1186b685345db92a762f060081c5609.poster.avif?t=1661251871\" width=620 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/e1186b685345db92a762f060081c5609.webm?t=1661251871\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1198310/extras/e1186b685345db92a762f060081c5609.mp4?t=1661251871\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
